    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "payment of a sum twice the original",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "借りた恩は倍返しするというのが彼の信条だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "契約書には、違約金は倍返しと明記されていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「今回の損害は倍返しで請求させていただきます！」と彼は息巻いた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": [
            {
              "text": "去り際、倍返しすると脅し、鬼の形相を見せたが、翌朝やって来て、低姿勢でわびを入れたので、俺は喜んで忘れることにした。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "玉手箱",
                "author": "A Golden Argosy",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "逆に、自分が行ったおふざけを倍返しする方法があります。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "王冠の重み",
                "author": "The Weight of the Crown",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "inflicting a revenge twice as hurtful (painful, costly, etc.) as the original misdeed",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "やられたらやり返す、倍返しだ！と心の中で誓った。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "ドラマの主人公は、敵に倍返しをすることで人気を博した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼からの裏切りに対し、倍返し以上の報復を考えている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
